description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'The ONLY Dumbbell Workout That You NEED (FULL BODY)' from the channel Mind Pump TV.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: The ONLY Dumbbell Workout That You Need! Minimal Equipment Needed for Maximum Gains!
Subscribe to Mind Pump TV: https://www.youtube.com/mindpumptv
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/mindpumpmedia/

Follow this Dumbbell Workout for Optimal Muscle Growth!

1. Walking Lunges 3x8-12 Reps
2. Dumbbell Rows 3x8-12 
3. Chest Press 3x8-12
4. Dumbbell Shoulder Press 3x8-12 
5. Dumbbell Bicep Curls Alternating 3x8-12
6. Dumbbell Tricep Extension 3x8-12 

Rest for 60 Seconds Between Sets.

For Added ABS Exercise add 3 Sets of 60 Second Planks.

Follow these with good form and achieve maximum health.
